chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to play?
yes
awesome! i'm starting at this spot just north of the twig that leads to the tiger's island
where should i go next?
Where the parrot and the  elephant can be found
gotcha! so, i'm heading southwest and left, and now i see the parrot and elephant
what's next, amigo?
now move to South East where the frog can be found
you got it, friend! after passing the 3 rocks southeast, i'm now at the frog's island
Now move to the west
alrighty! heading west and
surprise! i see a crocodile. next move?
lets jump on the back of the crocodile and cross
haha, adventurous! leap onto the crocodile, cross and now back on the big island with the elephant
where to now?
now lets move to the east where the giraffe is
roger that! heading east and now i'm with the giraffe
next step, please?
lets now move to the south west
ok, heading southwest
and i'm in front of a snake now. what's next?
Sneak around and get out of sight
hehe, sneaky sneaky
alright, got past the snake smoothly. now what?
we get the treasure
yay! 2 steps to the east and
ta-dah! found the treasure. we did it, buddy! *finished*

done

keep going in that direction and say hi to another white dog by a checkered picnic blanket
found it

done

onward!

ok done
